@Alex-302 
Required rule is in cookie filter, but not loaded with Safari Extension.
When I add the rule to user filter it works:
`||cookiebot.com^$domain=~cookiebot.com|~developer.opencv.fr`

Did not see a limitation in cookie_general though which excludes it. Do you know why?

--

Regarding assistant not showing : Reproduced. Cause is the site is setting the style:
iframe { z-index: 0 !important; }

Using a rule like is overwriting it:
apollo-news.net#$?#iframe#adguard-assistant-dialog { z-index: 2147483647 !important; }
